snippet.title: Filmmaker Tycoon - Announcement Trailer!
snippet.description:
Wishlist the Game on Steam now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/778010/ 

Filmmaker Tycoon is a next generation movie tycoon simulation game! You're the producer of your very own movie studio! Hire actors, build movie sets, make films, move up in the industry, and watch your finished films in Filmmaker Tycoon.

Website - http://filmmakertycoon.com/
Discord - https://discord.gg/Z9x6e74

#Tycoon #Simulation #Management
